ement Center  EPIC  at the University of Oregon named Dr  Dellinger s design of SP303W Spanish Conversation and Conversation  among the  Top Ten Courses Nationwide  in their 2007 College Board World Languages Best Practice Study in Spanish Language  Her SP305W Survey of Spanish Literature design garnered the same rating in EPIC s 2007 College Board World Languages Best Practice Study in Spanish Literature  Top Ten Courses Nationwide  The undergraduate courses submitted to EPIC for this study helped inform the revision of the Advanced Placement Exams in Spanish Language and Spanish Literature  Click here for a complete listing of Dr  Dellinger s awards and honors    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 